The Resident Electoral Commissioner (REC) in charge of FCT, Alhaji Yahaya Bello, has released phones numbers to help those facing difficulties locating their collection centres. In a statement he personally signed, Bello who said their offices will be open till Monday 11th February, for the collection of the PVCs, added that the days also included Saturday and Sunday. He said the time for the PVCs collection will be from 9am until 6pm daily. He said, “Those having difficulties locating their collection centres should please call INEC FCT Hot lines: 080153162663 or 08188241666. Only those with PVCs will be allowed to vote on Election Day.” As PVC collection ends today Nigerians in last minute rush for PVCs INEC bans food selling at polling units